message: Converted Tweet URLs to [[Template:Cite tweet|{{cite tweet}}]] Mistake? [[User talk:TheSandDoctor|msg TSD!]]
What the fuck does four segments mean?

There were dramatic and comedic elements in this series, but comedy-drama has a very specific definition and adding to the genres opens the floodgates to genre overload. I'm willing to allow science fantasy as that genre's general connotations are generally in line with this series, but technically I think it should probably not go beyond action-adventure or whatever is most frequently cited.
